=== Auto paragraphs
--- input
\declare:
  Paragraph = \record:
    content: \Text {primary}
  \end(record)

  Section = \record:
    title: \Text
    content: \paragraphs(\Paragraph, auto=true) {primary}:>
  \end(record)
\end(declare)

\fragment(type=\Section)

\Section(First Section)

Lorem ipsum

Dolor sit
amet

\Paragraph:
  consectetur adipiscing elit
\end(Paragraph)
